{"Version": "1.0.0", "LINES": [{"text": "where he is usually well received.\nBut, one night in December 1951,", "start": 120.24, "duration": 6.72, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "one night"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "December 1951"}], "sentiment": -0.25}, {"text": "Here, for example, we have a\nBrazilian Santa from 1907, a classic,", "start": 206.52, "duration": 4.6, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "1907"}], "sentiment": 0.16666666666666666}, {"text": "This one is perfect.", "start": 225.2, "duration": 1.68, "ents": [], "sentiment": 1.0}, {"text": "I don't have the Japanese one here,\nbut the whole world worships Santa Claus.", "start": 226.88, "duration": 4.96, "ents": [{"label_": "NORP", "text": "Japanese"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Santa Claus"}], "sentiment": 0.1}, {"text": "Among the thousands of representations\nof Santa Claus, one stands out.", "start": 244.44, "duration": 4.88, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "thousands"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Santa Claus"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The one of an early ancestor...", "start": 251.0, "duration": 2.4, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.1}, {"text": "The first ancestor of Santa\nClaus is found in mythology.", "start": 260.32, "duration": 3.84, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Santa\nClaus"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "A thousand years before Christ, there\nwas a God in the Scandinavian countries,", "start": 264.16, "duration": 5.48, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "A thousand years"}, {"label_": "NORP", "text": "Scandinavian"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "And this god, the first of\nhis kind, did the opposite.", "start": 288.52, "duration": 4.08, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}], "sentiment": 0.2833333333333333}, {"text": "He was the one who gave. So he\nhad a throne in heaven with two wolves.", "start": 292.6, "duration": 5.28, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "And he had two ravens,\nwhich he sent down to earth", "start": 297.88, "duration": 4.44, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}], "sentiment": -0.15555555555555559}, {"text": "That's between December\n17 to December 25.", "start": 308.04, "duration": 3.68, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "December\n17 to December 25"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "And then, in Rome, it\nstarted in the fifth century B.C.", "start": 311.72, "duration": 2.96, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Rome"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "the fifth century"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "B.C."}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "until the fourth century A.D.\nThere was a goddess called Strenia.", "start": 314.68, "duration": 5.32, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "the fourth century"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "A.D."}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Strenia"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "2000 years ago in Palestine,\na little baby was born,", "start": 487.12, "duration": 4.96, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "2000 years ago"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Palestine"}], "sentiment": -0.1875}, {"text": "In 354 AD, the Roman\nCatholic Church decided", "start": 504.2, "duration": 4.0, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "354"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "to place Jesus Christ\u2019s\nbirthday on December 25th,", "start": 508.2, "duration": 3.64, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "December 25th"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "And these three astonishing gifts\n- gold, frankincense and myrrh -", "start": 538.0, "duration": 6.44, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "myrrh -"}], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "one is especially central:\nthe one of Saint-Nicholas.", "start": 573.08, "duration": 4.68, "ents": [{"label_": "ORG", "text": "Saint-Nicholas"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In France, everyone knows the\nlegend of the three little children", "start": 662.8, "duration": 4.0, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "France"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}], "sentiment": -0.1875}, {"text": "And, after seven years, Saint Nicolas,\ncame to the inn or the butcher shop", "start": 674.0, "duration": 4.52, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "seven years"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Saint Nicolas"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "and resurrected\nthe three children.", "start": 678.52, "duration": 2.64, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In 1087 AD, faced with the\ninvasion of Turkey by the Saracens,", "start": 687.88, "duration": 5.0, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "1087 AD"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Turkey"}, {"label_": "NORP", "text": "Saracens"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "named Saint Nicolas-de-Port.\nHere, every year on December 6th,", "start": 705.6, "duration": 5.68, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Saint Nicolas-de-Port"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "every year"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "December 6th"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In addition to\nresurrecting the three boys,", "start": 752.32, "duration": 2.6, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "three"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Although Saint Nicholas brings\ngifts, he\u2019s also the one who punishes.", "start": 765.56, "duration": 4.84, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Saint Nicholas"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "One document recounts\nthat in December of 1552,", "start": 913.52, "duration": 3.08, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "One"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "December of 1552"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "when the city was besieged by Charles\nthe Fifth of the Holy Roman Empire,", "start": 916.6, "duration": 3.88, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Charles\nthe"}, {"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "Fifth"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "the Holy Roman Empire"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Later, every year on December 6th,\nwhich was the feast of Saint Nicholas,", "start": 928.92, "duration": 3.96, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "every year"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "December 6th"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Saint Nicholas"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The field of religion was the one of\nbaby Jesus, on the eve of December 24th.", "start": 946.08, "duration": 5.44, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "the eve of December 24th"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "What we have in the 1500\u2019s is\nan astonishing religious revolution", "start": 970.56, "duration": 6.88, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "1500"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "one and a half thousand years,", "start": 1002.2, "duration": 1.52, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "one and a half thousand years"}], "sentiment": -0.16666666666666666}, {"text": "And one of the things they\nagree on is that the cult of Saints", "start": 1006.64, "duration": 3.96, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Saints"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "as the object of one's prayers.", "start": 1018.64, "duration": 3.36, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "on December 6 were pushed back.\nThey were pushed back to Christmas,", "start": 1049.52, "duration": 4.08, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "December 6"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "Christmas"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "In 1570, a pastor spoke out against\nthe practice of giving gifts to children", "start": 1071.72, "duration": 4.88, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "1570"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The Saint Nicolas Market which is\nheld on December 6 was renamed.", "start": 1078.88, "duration": 4.6, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "December 6"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "These pilgrims first set foot on\nthe American continent in 1620", "start": 1268.88, "duration": 4.52, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}, {"label_": "NORP", "text": "American"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "1620"}], "sentiment": 0.125}, {"text": "In 1800, the situation in\nNew York City became dire.", "start": 1341.32, "duration": 4.2, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "1800"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "New York City"}], "sentiment": 0.13636363636363635}, {"text": "So one thing Pintard\nwas trying to do", "start": 1415.96, "duration": 2.68, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Pintard"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "And, for the first time, a new\nname appears in a drawing.", "start": 1469.6, "duration": 4.48, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}], "sentiment": 0.19318181818181818}, {"text": "There was a third member of\nthe New York Historical Society", "start": 1490.72, "duration": 2.68, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "third"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "the New York Historical Society"}], "sentiment": 0.04545454545454545}, {"text": "But a miniature sleigh,\nand eight tiny reindeer,", "start": 1520.76, "duration": 3.68, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "eight"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Later in the 19th century,", "start": 1558.56, "duration": 1.44, "ents": [{"label_": "TIME", "text": "Later in"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "the 19th century"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Christmas became one of\nthe great annual gatherings.", "start": 1833.12, "duration": 3.16, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "Christmas"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "annual"}], "sentiment": 0.8}, {"text": "One during which people\nhonored their own members,", "start": 1836.28, "duration": 3.04, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "One"}], "sentiment": 0.6}, {"text": "The Christmas tale tells the\nstory of how one of these misers", "start": 1894.4, "duration": 3.32, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "Christmas"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "The goose club concept in\nEngland is a very interesting one", "start": 1952.88, "duration": 3.8, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.65}, {"text": "is going to combine\nin the 19th century.", "start": 1986.8, "duration": 3.8, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "the 19th century"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "At first, the character bringing the\ngifts depended on where you lived.", "start": 1997.24, "duration": 3.88, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "But gradually, it\nbecame the same one.", "start": 2001.12, "duration": 3.16, "ents": [], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "and they enrolled Santa as\ntheir number one sales clerk.", "start": 2034.0, "duration": 3.68, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Santa"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Between the two world wars,\nSanta Claus became the ideal partner", "start": 2057.6, "duration": 4.04, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Santa Claus"}], "sentiment": 0.9}, {"text": "one of the most beautiful is that of\na child perched on a Parisian roof", "start": 2113.64, "duration": 4.16, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "NORP", "text": "Parisian"}], "sentiment": 0.675}, {"text": "The red Santa is\nthe traditional one", "start": 2150.32, "duration": 2.4, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Santa"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "that they call forth enemies. And\none of these enemies is totalitarianism.", "start": 2207.0, "duration": 7.48, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "When the Nazis take power in 1933,\ntheir first thought that the Nazis had,", "start": 2259.52, "duration": 8.32, "ents": [{"label_": "NORP", "text": "Nazis"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "1933"}, {"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}, {"label_": "NORP", "text": "Nazis"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "They want to move the celebration\nfrom December 25th to December 21st,", "start": 2283.4, "duration": 4.76, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "December 25th to December 21st"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "had to supply nearly 6 million\nprisoners of war to German factories", "start": 2330.0, "duration": 3.28, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "nearly 6 million"}, {"label_": "NORP", "text": "German"}], "sentiment": 0.05}, {"text": "He did two things. First, he wrote to\nchildren in the name of Santa Claus.", "start": 2354.92, "duration": 5.4, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}, {"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "First"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Santa Claus"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "In 1941, he organized a\nletter-writing competition", "start": 2366.24, "duration": 3.84, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "1941"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "There was to be only one winner per\nFrench district. The idea was simple:", "start": 2372.8, "duration": 6.36, "ents": [{"label_": "NORP", "text": "French"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "But first these Santas\nhad to take classes", "start": 2419.68, "duration": 3.2, "ents": [{"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}, {"label_": "ORG", "text": "Santas"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "For the first postwar Christmas\neve, Tino Rossi sings a song", "start": 2440.16, "duration": 3.48, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "the first postwar"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "Christmas\neve"}, {"label_": "LOC", "text": "Tino Rossi"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "What is certain is that the official\nSanta Claus Village was opened in 1985", "start": 2471.32, "duration": 5.04, "ents": [{"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Santa Claus Village"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "1985"}], "sentiment": 0.21428571428571427}, {"text": "More than 500,000 visitors\ncome here every year", "start": 2485.6, "duration": 3.4, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "More than 500,000"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "every year"}], "sentiment": 0.5}, {"text": "In 1951, in an underprivileged\nparish of Dijon, France,", "start": 2575.84, "duration": 4.44, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "1951"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Dijon"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "France"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "It\u2019s similar to the one carried\nout during Saturnalia festivities", "start": 2603.48, "duration": 3.68, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Saturnalia"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "And in the next 48 hours, these\nimages were seen all over France.", "start": 2621.36, "duration": 4.96, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "the next 48 hours"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "France"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "in which Santa was lowered from\none the tallest buildings in Dijon:", "start": 2644.28, "duration": 3.4, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Santa"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Dijon"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "Santa\u2019s official post office in\nRovaniemi received 17 million letters", "start": 2750.0, "duration": 4.08, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Santa"}, {"label_": "PERSON", "text": "Rovaniemi"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "17 million"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "from 100 countries in 1985.", "start": 2754.08, "duration": 2.48, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "100"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "1985"}], "sentiment": 0.0}, {"text": "And he asked his sister, Fran\u00e7oise\nMarette, to be Santa\u2019s first secretary.", "start": 2807.08, "duration": 4.84, "ents": [{"label_": "ORG", "text": "Fran\u00e7oise"}, {"label_": "GPE", "text": "Santa\u2019s"}, {"label_": "ORDINAL", "text": "first"}], "sentiment": 0.25}, {"text": "At 6, we entered primary\nschool, it\u2019s compulsory,", "start": 2881.04, "duration": 3.64, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "6"}], "sentiment": 0.4}, {"text": "Haha, they still believe in Saint-Nicholas.\nAnd then, after a year or two,", "start": 2887.68, "duration": 4.2, "ents": [{"label_": "GPE", "text": "Saint-Nicholas"}, {"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "two"}], "sentiment": 0.2}, {"text": "Who represents the true spirit\nof Christmas, the original one?", "start": 2940.92, "duration": 4.2, "ents": [{"label_": "DATE", "text": "Christmas"}], "sentiment": 0.3625}, {"text": "But one of the absolute constants\nof the history of Christmas", "start": 3014.0, "duration": 3.48, "ents": [{"label_": "CARDINAL", "text": "one"}, {"label_": "DATE", "text": "Christmas"}], "sentiment": 0.2}, {"text": "but none of it is a 100% for sure.", "start": 3079.04, "duration": 2.64, "ents": [{"label_": "PERCENT", "text": "100%"}], "sentiment": 0.5}], "VIDEO_ID": "UE8UcCohuSs", "VIDEO_DATA": [{"videoId": "UE8UcCohuSs", "channelId": "UCW39zufHfsuGgpLviKh297Q", "description": "Santa Claus is a global icon. But where did this friendly old man in a red suit who brings gifts for children actually come from?", "title": "The true story of Santa Claus | DW Documentary", "publishedAt": "2022-12-24T17:00:11Z"}]}